====Usage notes====
Used to form benefactive and aditive verbs from other verbs (either of Bantu or Arabic origin), e.g., ''[[lipa]]'' ([[pay]]) --> ''[[lipia]]'' (pay for); ''[[jibu]]'' ([[answer]]) --> ''[[jibia]]'' (answer to/for).  This affix is subject to vowel harmony: verbs with root vowels /e/ and /o/ take {{l|sw|-ea}}, e.g., ''[[soma]]'' ([[read]]) --> ''[[somea]]'' (read to/for s.o).

